al; line-height: 150%" class="western">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <br />  </p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <img src="file:///C:/Program%20Files/OpenOffice.org%203/Basis/share/gallery/rulers/grnrulr3.gif" border="0" alt="" width="603" height="11" align="LEFT" /><br /><br />  </p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">W przypadku  zainteresowania naszą ofertą wymiany oprogramowania lub wymiany i  szkolenia/wdrożenia, prosimy o kontakt:</font></font></p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">&nbsp;</p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; line-height: 150%" class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2"><strong><br /></strong></font></font></p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">telefoniczny: (042)  648-03-34 (Michał Pertyński)</font></font></p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <font size="3"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">email:  </font></font><font color="#0000ff"><u><a href="mailto:michal.pertynski@arisco.pl"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">michal.pertynski@arisco.pl</font></a></u></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">   </font></font></font>  </p>  <p style="text-indent: 1.27cm; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%" class="western">  <font size="3"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">www:  </font></font><font color="#0000ff"><u><a href="http://www.arisco.pl/szkolenia"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">www.arisco.pl/szkolenia</font></a></u></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">  </font></font><font size="2"> </font></font>  </p>', '1256025281', '1354695051', '', 779, '', '